<tile>
    <visual>
        <binding template="TileMedium" branding="nameAndLogo" hint-textStacking="center">
            <text hint-style="caption" hint-wrap="true">Play music at home or on the go.</text>
        </binding>
        <binding template="TileWide" branding="nameAndLogo" hint-textStacking="center">
            <text hint-style="body" hint-wrap="true">Play music at home or on the go.</text>
        </binding>
        <binding template="TileLarge" branding="nameAndLogo" hint-textStacking="top">
            <text hint-style="title" hint-wrap="true"></text>
            <text hint-style="title" hint-wrap="true">Play music at home or on the go.</text>
        </binding>
    </visual>
</tile>
